<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/style.css' />
      <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/animate.css/3.7.0/animate.min.css">
      <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/fomantic-ui@2.7.2/dist/semantic.min.css">
      <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-ggOyR0iXCbMQv3Xipma34MD+dH/1fQ784/j6cY/iJTQUOhcWr7x9JvoRxT2MZw1T" crossorigin="anonymous">
  </head>
  <body>
  <div class="ui fixed top sticky  stackable  menu">
    <div class="item">
      <img src="/images/world.svg">
      <h1>Double Bits</h1>
    </div>
    <a class="item" href="#1" >Payouts</a>
    <a class=" item" href="#2">Testimonials</a>
    <a class=" orange item" href="#3">About us</a>

  </div>
<div class="d">
    <h1>Double your Bitcoins in 3hours</h1>
<img src="/images/growth.svg">
    <h2>Min:0.001 BTC</h2>
    <h2>Max:2 BTC</h2>
    <p id="yes" class="ui inverted purple message"></p>

</div>
<h2 class="ui red header" style="text-align: center">Just put your wallet address below to get started</h2>
  <p class="ui red message" style="text-align: center">Your wallet address will serve as your Login</p>
  <form class="ui  fluid form" method="post">
      <div class="field">
          <input type="text" placeholder="Bitcoin Address" id="a" oninput="validate()" name="btc">
          <button class="ui large inverted primary button" type="submit">To Dashboard</button>
          <div class="ui pointing red basic label" id="n">
              <%= message %>
          </div>
      </div>
  </form>
  <br>
  <br>
<div class="c">
    <h1>REFERRAL</h1>
   <center> <img src="/images/collaboration.svg"></center>
<h2  class="animated bounce delay-2s infinite">Get 10% of your referrals deposit</h2>
<p>Refer friends and earn.<br>Login to the dashboard to get your personal link</p>

</div>

<br>
  <br>
  <h2 style="color: purple;font-weight: bolder;text-align: center" id="1">Recent Payouts</h2>
<p style="color: lawngreen;text-align: center;font-weight: bolder;"> check out below the latest<br>Payouts confirmed on the blockchain</p>
  <table style="width:100%">
      <tr>
          <th>Amount<i class="fab fa-bitcoin" style="color: orange"></i></th>
          <th>Time<i class="fas fa-clock" style="color: cyan"></i></th>
          <th>Address<i class="fas fa-address-card" style="color:whitesmoke"></i></th>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <% for(var i=0; i < users.length; i++) { %>
      <tr>
          <td><%= users[i].amount %></td>
          <td><%= users[i].time %></td>
          <td><a href="https://www.blockchain.com/btc/address/<%= users[i].withdrawadd %>"><%= users[i].withdrawadd %></a></td>
      </tr>
      <% } %>
  </table>

<br>
  <br>

  <h2 style="color: purple;font-weight: bolder;text-align: center" id="2">Testimonials</h2>
  <br>
  <br>
  <div class="bd-example">
      <div id="carouselExampleCaptions" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
          <ol class="carousel-indicators">
              <li data-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
              <li data-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-slide-to="1"></li>
              <li data-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-slide-to="2"></li>
          </ol>
          <div class="carousel-inner" style="background:linear-gradient(to left,blue,cyan)">
              <div class="carousel-item active">
                  <img src="/images/boss.svg" class="d-block w-100" alt="..." style="height: 5cm">
                  <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                      <h5 style="color: red">Mike</h5>
                      <p style="color: black">Fast and Profitable</p>
                  </div>
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                  <img src="/images/girl.svg" class="d-block w-100" alt="..." style="height: 5cm">
                  <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                      <h5 style="color: red">Cynthia</h5>
                      <p style="color: black">Trusted</p>
                  </div>
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                  <img src="/images/boy.svg" class="d-block w-100" alt="..." style="height: 5cm">
                  <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                      <h5 style="color: red">Donald</h5>
                      <p style="color: black">easy and reliable</p>
                  </div>
              </div>
          </div>
          <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleCaptions" role="button" data-slide="prev">
              <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
              <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
          </a>
          <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleCaptions" role="button" data-slide="next">
              <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
              <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
          </a>
      </div>
  </div>



<br>
  <br>



  <h2 style="color: purple;font-weight: bolder;text-align: center" id="3">About us</h2>
  <br>
  <br>

  <div class="ui styled  fluid accordion">
      <div class="active title">
          <i class="red dropdown icon"></i>
          What is Double Bits
      </div>
      <div class="active content">
          <p style="color: green"> Double Bits is a unique platform where you get to double your Bitcoins in just 3hours</p>
      </div>
      <div class="title">
          <i class="purple dropdown icon"></i>
         How can i start?
      </div>
      <div class="content">
          <p>You can start by login in to the dashboard using your own Bitcoin Address where you will get a personal deposit address to fund your account</p>
      </div>
      <div class="title">
          <i class="orange dropdown icon"></i>
          When will i get my profit
      </div>
      <div class="content">
          <p>Normally after a deposit,Bitcoins get doubled after 3 hours</p>
          <p>After which they are automatically credited to your account for withdrawals</p>
      </div>
  </div>






<br>
  <br>
  <br>

  <div class="card-footer text-muted bg-dark ">
      <h2><i class="purple copyright icon"></i>Double Bits</h2>
      <button class="ui facebook button">
          <i class="facebook icon"></i>
          Facebook
      </button>
      <button class="ui twitter button">
          <i class="twitter icon"></i>
          Twitter
      </button>
      <button class="ui google plus button">
          <i class="google plus icon"></i>
          Google Plus
      </button>
  </div>




